main_body:
Article 1 of Regulation (EEC) No 4007/87 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in the first subparagraph, '31 December 1992' with regard to Spain shall be replaced by '31 December 1993';
2. in the second subparagraph, '31 December 1992' with regard to Portugal shall be replaced by '31 December 1993'.
